text: Sébastien Lecornu (; born 11 June 1986) is a French politician. He is in the government of Prime Minister Élisabeth Borne as Minister of the Armed Forces since 2022.Victor Boiteau (20 May 2022), Changement dans la continuité: Darmanin, Le Maire, Attal… Ces ministres qui remettent ça dans le gouvernement Borne Libération. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Normandy Category:People from Eure
